headline: Is Target (TGT) Pricing Reflect Short Term Rebound Or Longer Term Weakness
summary: If you are wondering whether Target's current share price reflects good value or lingering concerns, this article walks through what the numbers are saying about the stock. Target recently closed at US$100.51, with returns of 2.5% over the last 7 days and 9.0% over the last 30 days, while the 1 year return sits at a 24.7% decline and the 3 and 5 year returns show declines of 28.7% and 40.9% respectively.
